      "description": "Looking for an affordable, no-frills ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it shows its age with some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections, but it runs and drives, making it a smart pick for budget-conscious buyers or a first car. It's been kept operational and is ready for daily use. Come take it for a spin and see the value for yourself!",
