    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid, Dependable, and Ready for the Road! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in genuinely good condition \u2014 regularly serviced and showing only the normal, expected wear you'd find on a well-loved, consistently driven car. It runs great, looks presentable, and has been cared for by an attentive owner. If you're looking for a reliable ride that won't let you down, this one deserves a serious look. Come take it for a spin \u2014 you won't be disappointed!",
