    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Great Condition & Ready to Roll \u2014 A Reliable Ride You Can Count On! \u2014 Don't miss this well-maintained gem! This car is in good condition \u2014 it's been taken care of, runs smoothly, and presents nicely inside and out. You'll find the usual minor signs of everyday use, but nothing that affects performance or enjoyment. Whether you're commuting, road-tripping, or just looking for a dependable daily driver, this one checks all the boxes. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with every potential buyer. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple noticeable scratches, dents, and areas of paint fading or chipping. The interior is similarly worn, with tears or heavy staining on the upholstery and signs of long-term use throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs to bring it to a reliable, road-ready state \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs parts. There are no major hidden surprises here; what you see is what you get. This is priced accordingly to reflect its current state, and we encourage any serious buyer to inspect it thoroughly before purchasing.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in mint condition, and prospective buyers will be thoroughly impressed with what they find. The exterior is immaculate \u2014 the paint retains its deep, original luster with absolutely no visible scratches, chips, dents, or fading. All body panels are perfectly aligned, and the glass is crystal clear with no chips or cracks. The interior is equally pristine: upholstery shows no wear, staining, or damage, all controls and electronics function flawlessly, and the cabin retains a fresh, clean feel throughout. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly with no unusual noises, leaks, or warning lights. Service records are up to date, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. Tires have excellent tread remaining and all four are evenly worn. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that truly lives up to the 'mint' designation \u2014 it is as close to new as a used car can get.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we are committed to full honesty with every potential buyer. The exterior shows noticeable wear \u2014 expect some surface scratches, minor dents, and areas where the paint has faded or lost its luster. There is no significant rust, but the body does show its age. The interior is functional but worn, with visible scuffing on the seats, some fading on the dashboard trim, and general signs of regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 minor maintenance items are likely due, and buyers should budget for routine servicing. All major systems are operational, but this is not a turnkey, worry-free vehicle. It is best suited for a buyer who understands they are purchasing a used car that will require some investment of time and money to bring up to a higher standard. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    }
